              <p><font size="2" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><strong><font size="3">MAY 2003</font><br>
Vol 2, No. 6 </strong></font></p>
              <p><FONT face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size=3><B>CONSORTIUM EVOLUTION</b></font></p>
              <div align="center" class="style2 style25">
